## **3. Ticketly (Twig/PHP Version)**

```markdown
# Ticketly (Twig/PHP Version)

Ticketly is a PHP-based ticket management web application using Twig templating. Users can create, edit, and delete tickets while tracking their statuses. The project focuses on server-side rendering with a clean and responsive design.

## Features
- User authentication and session management
- Create, edit, and delete tickets
- Dashboard for ticket statistics (total, open, closed)
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile
- Server-side rendering using Twig templates

## Technologies Used
- PHP 8.x
- Twig templating engine
- CSS3 and JavaScript for interactivity
- Composer for dependency management

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ticketly.git
